dermaus. Its popularity was further reinforced in the 1930s as the name of a character in the novels of  Dornford Yates ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Adelle Selvesla was born about 1040. She had at least 1 daughter with Erard de Furnes. She died in 1100, in Ardres, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France, at the age of 61."},"et":{"Abt 1040–1100":"umbes 1040–1100","1040–1061":"1040–1061","1060–1127":"1060–1127","1040–1100":"1040–1100","1127":"1127","Abt 1040":"umbes 1040","1100":"1100","1040":"1040","Abt 1060":"umbes 1060","1061":"1061","1060":"1060","Notre-Dame-de-Grâce-et-Saint-Omer d'Ardres, Saint-Omer, Ardres, France":"Ardres, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"Abt 1040–1100":"noin 1040–1100","1040–1061":"1040–1061","1060–1127":"1060–1127","1040–1100":"1040–1100","1127":"1127","Abt 1040":"noin 1040","1100":"1100","1040":"1040","Abt 1060":"noin 1060","1061":"1061","1060":"1060","Notre-Dame-de-Grâce-et-Saint-Omer d'Ardres, Saint-Omer, Ardres, France":"Ardres, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Ranska"},"fr":{"Abt 1040–1100":"environ 1040–1100","1040–1061":"1040–1061","1060–1127":"1060–1127","1040–1100":"1040–1100","1127":"1127","Abt 1040":"environ 1040","1100":"1100","1040":"1040","Abt 1060":"environ 1060","1061":"1061","1060":"1060","Notre-Dame-de-Grâce-et-Saint-Omer d'Ardres, Saint-Omer, Ardres, France":"Ardres, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France","lifeSummary":"Adelle Selvesla est née environ 1040. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Erard de Furnes. Elle est décédée en 1100, à Ardres, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France, à l’âge de 61 ans."},"de":{"Abt 1040–1100":"um 1040–1100","1040–1061":"1040–1061","1060–1127":"1060–1127","1040–1100":"1040–1100","1127":"1127","Abt 1040":"um 1040","1100":"1100","1040":"1040","Abt 1060":"um 1060","1061":"1061","1060":"1060","Notre-Dame-de-Grâce-et-Saint-Omer d'Ardres, Saint-Omer, Ardres, France":"Ardres, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Adelle Selvesla wurde um 1040 geboren. Sie hatte mit E